msgid "Un job es una tarea programada con schedule daily, weekly, monthly o expresión cron. Al ejecutarse, emite un evento interno o realiza un POST a una URL externa."
msgstr "A job is a scheduled task with daily, weekly, monthly, or cron expression scheduling. On execution, it emits an internal event or performs a POST to an external URL."

#: lib/streamflix_web_web/live/docs_live.ex:969
